track_notes: Long walk in the guarrigue, nice place to be!

From the village La Foux, there are many footpath to reach the Col Bas on the crest that lead to the summit. You can park only one car on the small road. (plenty room at La Foux). The sloope is a bit hard  100 meters, after the water source! You must follow the many cairn. There is plenty room for antenna.

Long walk to reach the trig point, not difficult; this walk is clockwise at the Col des Portes, try to find a best path to the crest, the way down is easy but you must look and follow the cain until you reach Col Bas; in hot weather get some water and behave fire alert. info@f6hbi
